   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Relief For Refugees in Greece&apos;s Largest Camp</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Since 2016, we have provided dignified psychosocial support to people living in a prolonged state of emergency in Ritsona Refugee camp.  Offering safe spaces to gather, play, learn, and generally regain a semblance of normalcy, we endeavor to be a beacon of light and hope to children and youth who have experienced trauma and extreme hardship. Activities range from English classes to football tournaments to music workshops, based on requests from the community.</narrative>
  </description>
